VALUES
	(1,'WHO','Shannon and Christian Mayer a husband and wife team that have an extensive background in Theater, Dance and Music. Together, they have been working with young people for over 20 years','2015-10-12 00:52:30'),
	(2,'WHAT','A Children\'s Theater that focuses on youth between the ages of 4-18.','2015-10-12 01:36:31'),
	(3,'WHEN','We have ongoing classes that support Musical Theater, Acting and Dance and we produce 8 Broadway, Jr. and Broadway kids shows a year in our 90 seat black box theater.','2015-10-12 00:54:15'),
